  "datePublished": "2026-01-01",
  "description": "To sanitize is to reduce microbes on tools, jars, trays, or other equipment to a level considered safe for [food-safe](./food-safe.md) use. In [home gardening](../_index.md) for [sprouts](./sprout.md) and [microgreens](../topics/microgreens/index.md), sanitizing is a routine step before each growing cycle because the warm, moist conditions that support germination also support bacterial growth.",
